OL,7,FA mum-of-three whose unborn baby
OL,8,Freceived a life-saving blood
OL,9,Ftransfusion while he was still in the
OL,10,Fwomb is encouraging more people to
OL,11,Fconsider .
OL,13,FNate Davies and his mother Rebecca
OL,14,Fwere diagnosed with rhesus disease, a
OL,15,Frare and potentially deadly condition
OL,16,Fwhich sees the mother's blood produce
OL,17,Fantibodies which attack the baby's
OL,18,Fblood.
