OL,7,FNate, from, received a blood
OL,8,Ftransfusion at 28 weeks in the womb,
OL,9,Fthen another when he was just a day
OL,10,Fold, after being delivered prematurely.
OL,12,FNow seven years old, Rebecca said she
OL,13,Fis "very, very grateful" to the blood
OL,14,Fdonors who saved her son's life.
