OL,7,FExplaining how the procedure worked,
OL,8,FRebecca told ITV Cymru Wales: "They
OL,9,Finsert the needle through the stomach
OL,10,Finto the umbilical cord. Within
OL,11,Fminutes they get the results and know
OL,12,Fexactly how much they need to give to
OL,13,Fthe baby.
OL,15,F"It turns out he was quite anaemic and
OL,16,Fif he didn't have that blood while I
OL,17,Fwas pregnant it wouldn't have been the
OL,18,Fsame outcome.
