OL,7,F"He was quite poorly, so was covered
OL,8,Fin wires and strapped to different
OL,9,Fmachines and things, but knowing that
OL,10,Fhe has that blood is just such a
OL,11,Frelief because if it's not there,
OL,12,Fthere's nothing you can do.
OL,14,F"That's the thing that saved his life
OL,15,Fis the blood before and after he was
OL,16,Fborn."
