OL,7,FA 10-time blood donor herself, Rebecca
OL,8,Fadded: "It's a life-saving department,
OL,9,Freally. If you can donate, please go
OL,10,Fand do it, it doesn't take long. If
OL,11,Fyou're eligible, go and save lives."
OL,13,FThe needs around 350 donations every
OL,14,Fday to meet demand in hospitals across
OL,15,FWales.
OL,17,FIt is estimated that one donation can
OL,18,Fhelp save up to three lives.
