OL,8,Fa steady flow is never guaranteed and
OL,9,Fthe service always needs more people
OL,10,Fto volunteer.
OL,12,FJayne Davey, head of collection
OL,13,Fservices, said: "Throughout life
OL,14,Fthere'll be all sorts of things that
OL,15,Fstop us being able to donate.
