OL,7,FTogether, husband and wife Siobhan and
OL,8,FGareth Bickerton have donated blood
OL,9,Fwell over 50 times.
OL,11,F"I've got O negative blood so that can
OL,12,Fbe given to anybody and it's usually
OL,13,Fused for neonates so I think why
OL,14,Fwouldn't I?" Siobhan said.
OL,16,FGareth added: "We both think it's so
OL,17,Fimportant that we really do push the
OL,18,Fmessage out that more people should do
OL,19,Fit.
