OL,7,F"It's so easy to do, it's not
OL,8,Fstressful, the staff are lovely and
OL,9,Fit's a myth that we do it for the free
OL,10,Fbiscuits."
OL,12,FSteve Hicks has been donating his
OL,13,Fblood for around 30 years.
OL,15,F"It's quite a simple process, it
OL,16,Fdoesn't take too long but if you think
OL,17,Fabout it it's actually a life-saving
OL,18,Factivity," he said.
